###
### LIFE THREATENING SITUATIONS AND RescueS THEREFROM.
###

SavesLife ?saver ?savee:
   [ThreateningSituation ?savee ?threat]
   [IntroduceThreat ?savee ?threat]
   [Rescue ?savee ?saver ?threat]
[end]

